snippet.title: Coke - Amstrad CPC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Developed by Swift Software and released in 1989, the goal is to shoot Coke cans to score points before the "Thirst" counter reaches 9. There is absolutely no archived information about this obscure Amstrad CPC game. We don't even know if it was even licensed by The Coca-Cola Company. This game is shrouded in mystery, as this is all the info I know from CPC-Power. There isn't even a gameplay video until I uploaded this one.
